divs: Sighting DetailsI got around at 1.30 in my back garden to smoke a cigarette as i look't in the sky to the west 85' o, to the Great Square the star from the right hand sight on top disappeared first and its looks like a round Disc (two or more ?) past its way, after a couple of seconds the second star disappeared. the sky was very clear, i could only see a black shadow from it. Its flew from the west to the east. it must be a very high altitude I mention it looks very big, compare to a airplane from a couple of mm to the distance of 10 cm. on front of the two shadows was a flashing light very slow flying it make a halve circle. At an higher altitude i saw like a star flying what i saw often in the past time. I was very excited and scared in the same time, because they must be really Big. I really dont know what's going on there ....?
